    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><dateline><placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> Dec<hi rend="superscript">r.</hi> 8<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>
                        1772.</dateline><salute>Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>various avocations at home after my long absence prevented me from sooner making
                    my acknowledgemen<add place="above">ts</add> for the great civility I
                    experienced the last summer at your house: it was a continuance of the
                    hospitality <placeName ref="pl0711">The Highlands</placeName> are so noted
                        for.<note type="editorial">Pennant stayed with Mackenzie for around four
                        days during the second leg of his 1772 tour: see <bibl type="editorial"><title ref="bi0010">A tour in Scotland 1772, part II</title></bibl>
                        (1776), p.67.</note> Please to accept my best thanks for the pleasure I
                    enjoyed while at <placeName ref="pl0287">Delvin</placeName> which I shall be
                    happy to return to any of your friends who should ever visit these parts. Please
                    to present my compliments to <persName ref="pe1998">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi></persName> &amp; <persName ref="pe1999">Miss
                        Mackenzie</persName></p>
                <closer><salute>&amp; think me with great <lb/>regard <lb/>Sir Your obliged &amp;
                        <lb/>most obedient humble Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Thomas Pennant</persName></signed></closer>


                <postscript>
                    <p>Decem<hi rend="superscript">r.</hi> 8<hi rend="superscript">th.</hi> 1772</p>
                    <p><persName ref="pe0232">Thomas Pennant Esq<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></persName></p>
                    <p>If any answer to be sent to <persName ref="pe0228">M<hi rend="superscript">r
                            </hi>Paton</persName>
                        <persName ref="pl0696">Custom house</persName></p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>To</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>J Mackenzie esq<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></addrLine>
                        <addrLine>at Delvin</addrLine>
                    </address></p>
            </div>
